{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "16", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "20", "M": "26", "S": "17"}}, "news": [{"title": "Janus Living eyes $5 billion valuation in US IPO", "para": "Senior housing REIT Janus Living is targeting a valuation of up to $5 billion in its U.S. IPO, seeking to raise $740 million. Despite market volatility, the company, carved out from Healthpeak Properties, is proceeding with its listing. Janus owns 34 senior housing communities, primarily in Florida and Texas, catering to rising demand driven by aging demographics.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/janus-living-aims-for-5-billion-valuation-with-upcoming-us-ipo-amid-market-volatility/129613410?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-39326/129613410.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "international"}, {"title": "NCLAT permits Chronos Properties to renew bank guarantee, valid for next six months", "para": "The NCLAT has allowed Brookfield-backed Chronos Properties to replace its expired bank guarantee within a week for the IL&FS Bandra Kurla Complex property. The tribunal also extended its interim order preventing IL&FS from creating third-party rights on its headquarters. Chronos' bid was initially Rs 1,080 crore, later revised by IL&FS to Rs 1,481 crore.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/nclat-allows-chronos-properties-to-renew-bank-guarantee-for-ilfs-property-acquisition/129613252?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-34248/129613252.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "DRA Homes acquires 3.91 acres land in Chennai for \u20b949.70 crore", "para": "DRA Homes has purchased 3.91 acres of land in Karanai, Chennai. The cost of the land was \u20b949.70 crore. The company intends to build a mid-segment residential community on this site. The estimated value of the homes to be developed is around \u20b9500 crore. This acquisition strengthens DRA Homes' development plans in Chennai.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/dra-homes-acquires-3-91-acres-land-in-chennai-for-49-70-crore/129613946?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-264112/129613946.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}]}